## 3. Mapping Rules

- Do not delete old documents automatically.
- Do not silently merge conflicting documents.
- Do not invent missing facts.
- Mark unknown facts as `UNKNOWN`.
- Mark non-applicable areas as `N/A`.
- Record conflicts in `docs/DOC_CONFLICTS.md`.

